About Us

We aren’t your typical investment firm.

From day one, we’ve believed in the power of consumer technology to measurably improve billions of lives across the globe.

From housing to healthcare, food delivery to finances, education to entertainment and transportation, we're investing in the world’s most promising entrepreneurs to solve the world’s most pressing problems.

Animation trigger

We are G dwater.

The world’s first regenerative investment platform.

But what does that even mean? Let us explain.

We believe that for venture to succeed these days, betting big on excellent entrepreneurs isn’t enough. So we’re building a totally new system of entrepreneurship—one where realizing returns is no longer the final step in the process. Instead, our model starts earlier and extends further than any other firm you’ll find.

01white bg

Genesis is the initial step in our closed-loop process.

It democratizes software, systems, and wisdom for entrepreneurs everywhere, lowering the bar of entry, and allowing more promising business ideas anywhere in the world to explore the field, learn best practices, and find their initial footing.

02white bg

The next step is Capital, where we invest in the very best world-changing companies and entrepreneurs.

We accelerate teams that are ready to scale, and help them move from successful startups to market leaders.

03white bg

Then there’s Collective,the final step in our model.

This is where we close the loop, funneling Goodwater’s profits back into our Portfolio Companies, increasing the accessibility and affordability of their products for people in need. It’s how we ensure that our profits and companies improve the lives of communities around the world.

Our Manifesto

At Goodwater we seek out exceptional entrepreneurs and help them cultivate the success they deserve.

At Goodwater we don’t chase wealth or fame. We chase big dreams that have the potential to change the world. These are the dreams of entrepreneurs whose consumer tech startups are transforming the way we live, work, eat, and play—for the better.

From day one we’ve believed in the power of consumer technology to measurably improve billions of lives across the globe. From housing to healthcare, food delivery to finances, education to entertainment and transportation, we're committed to guiding the world’s most promising entrepreneurs to solve the world’s most pressing problems.

Our software-enabled model combined with our values-driven investment practices ensures consistently exceptional outcomes not only for entrepreneurs, employees and LP’s, but also for society at large.

We’re reinventing what it means to be a venture capital firm by acting as a regenerative investment platform that democratizes access to capital and continually reinvests insights and profits back into the companies we serve, so that they can in turn serve even more people.

We are Goodwater and we empower exceptional entrepreneurs everywhere to change the world for good.
